PROJECT INFORMATION

Project Name: Aureum Programming Language
Version: 0.1.0 (MVP)
Release Date: March 25, 2026
Description: AI-native programming language combining Python syntax with 
             Rust performance, implementing BitNet b1.58 and Matryoshka 
             optimization techniques.

TECHNICAL ACHIEVEMENTS

- BitNet b1.58: Ternary computation with 2-bit weight compression
- Matryoshka Operator: Adaptive scale processing
- Performance: 10-20x faster than traditional FP32
- Memory: 16x reduction compared to FP32
- Architecture: Hybrid Python (frontend) + Rust (backend)

Created with 💛 in Resende, RJ, Brazil
